sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway<br/>(HTTPRoute)
    participant APIServer as API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Processor as Processor<br/>9090/TCP
    participant InfGW as Inference Gateway<br/>(llm-d/GIE/EPP)
    participant GC as Garbage Collector<br/>9091/TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as Operator Controller

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Batch Job Submission
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/files<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
        Gateway->>APIServer: Forward (HTTPRoute)
        APIServer->>S3: Upload input file<br/>S3 access key, TLS
        S3-->>APIServer: Upload confirmed
        APIServer->>DB: Store file metadata<br/>Connection URL credentials
        APIServer-->>Gateway: File ID
        Gateway-->>Client: File ID response

        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/batches<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
        Gateway->>APIServer: Forward (HTTPRoute)
        APIServer->>DB: Create batch job record<br/>Connection URL credentials
        APIServer-->>Gateway: Batch job ID
        Gateway-->>Client: Batch ID response
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Processor,S3: Flow 2: Batch Job Processing
        Processor->>DB: Dequeue pending job<br/>Connection URL credentials
        DB-->>Processor: Job details
        Processor->>S3: Download input file<br/>S3 access key, TLS
        S3-->>Processor: Input data (JSONL)
        loop For each inference request (AIMD concurrency)
            Processor->>InfGW: POST inference request<br/>Optional Bearer Token, TLS/mTLS
            InfGW-->>Processor: Inference result
        end
        Processor->>S3: Upload output file<br/>S3 access key, TLS
        Processor->>DB: Update job status → completed
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 238)
        Note over GC,DB: Flow 3: Garbage Collection
        GC->>DB: Query expired jobs/files<br/>Connection URL credentials
        DB-->>GC: Expired records
        GC->>S3: Delete expired files<br/>S3 access key, TLS
        GC->>DB: Remove expired records
    end

    rect rgb(245, 240, 255)
        Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Operator Reconciliation
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: LLMBatchGateway CR event<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA token
        Controller->>Controller: Helm chart rendering<br/>(in-process, specToHelmValues)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Server-Side Apply resources<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Apply confirmed
        Controller->>Controller: deleteOrphanedResources()
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Delete orphaned resources<br/>(if any disabled features)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
        Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Flow 5: Cross-Namespace Secret Sync
        Controller->>K8sAPI: List ReferenceGrants<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Matching grants
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Read source Secret<br/>(cross-namespace)
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Secret data
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update {name}-credentials<br/>in CR namespace (SSA)
    end
